my_app.views.authenticate_user(request)[source]

This method will take a http request and returns a http response. For example HTML documents. Authenticates the user with build in authentication system

Parameters:

request – http request

Returns:

if user is not authenticated http response login.html. Goes to the login page. else user is authenticated http response user.html. Goes to user page.
